                    "body": "bq. Apologies if I'm reopening a debate that's been settled, but just because appending isn't supported on all filesystems, why does that mean we can't allow it on filesystems where it is supported?\r\n\r\nWe can, it's just that it's less useful :-) Nobody opposed when we started deprecating it, but we can un-deprecate if desired.",
